      "body": "Not sure if we want to prefix all compile-time constants in this codebase with `BITCOIN_` this seems verbose and violates https://isocpp.github.io/CppCoreGuidelines/CppCoreGuidelines#enum5-dont-use-all_caps-for-enumerators\n\nWhy not use PascalCase or so?",
